# When To Trigger

- When dealing with files that read or handles ".sql"-files.
- When dealing with in-code queries that creates or modifies tables and views.

# Don't modify database schema

- NEVER make unrequested database changes.
- NEVER change any database schemas (for example table names, column names, view names and so on) unless explicitly asked to do so.
